// Player Statistics Endpoints

### Get All Player Statistics
GET http://localhost:3000/api/player-statistics

### Get Top Players by Activity
GET http://localhost:3000/api/player-statistics/leaderboard/activity

### Get Top Players by Activity (limit 5)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/player-statistics/leaderboard/activity?limit=5

### Get Top Players by Net Worth
GET http://localhost:3000/api/player-statistics/leaderboard/wealth

### Get Top Players by Net Worth (limit 5)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/player-statistics/leaderboard/wealth?limit=5

### Get Player Statistics
GET http://localhost:3000/api/players/2/statistics

### Get Player Statistics (not found)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/players/99999/statistics

### Get Player Statistics (invalid ID)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/players/invalid/statistics

### Create Player Statistics
POST http://localhost:3000/api/players/1/statistics

### Create Player Statistics (invalid ID)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/players/invalid/statistics

### Delete Player Statistics
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/players/2/statistics

### Delete Player Statistics (not found)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/players/99999/statistics
